The paper deals with the transmission of data over wireless networks, which is a topic that falls under the Information Theory (cs.IT) and Networking and Internet Architecture (cs.NI) sub-categories. The use of multiple antennas and linear precoding techniques also suggests that the paper may be relevant to the Systems and Control (cs.SY) sub-category. Additionally, the paper discusses the energy efficiency of the proposed transmission strategies, which could be relevant to the Multimedia (cs.MM) and Machine Learning (cs.LG) sub-categories.
